{"TopicId":170230,"ForumId":20,"TopicTitle":"Auto-hide UI when taking a screenshot?","CreatedByName":"Pipcard","CreatedById":2541,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-01-29T10:13:41Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Pipcard","CreatedById":2541,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-01-29T10:13:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs there a mod that lets you toggle the option to automatically hide the UI when F1 is pressed (like a blink)? It\u0027s easier to think about just pressing F1 instead of pressing F2, then F1, then F2 again when you\u0027re doing a propulsive landing on a planet or moon and want to take a nice screenshot moments before touchdown.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222018-01-29T10:16:18Z\u0022 title=\u002201/29/2018 10:16  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00226 yr\u0022\u003EJanuary 29, 2018\u003C/time\u003E by Pipcard\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DrLicor","CreatedById":165712,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-01-29T10:37:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHaven\u0027t seen that mod around sadly. I like the idea. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Rocket In My Pocket","CreatedById":154640,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-01-29T13:06:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBetterTimeWarp helps somewhat, as you can throw the game into like 1/10 speed slow motion and then you have all the time in the world to set up the perfect screenshot.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n(Not sure if it would work using the in game screenshot function as I use Steam\u0027s, but you can also pause the game via Escape, then toggle the UI, then take a screenshot.)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed721812901\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/154935-131-bettertimewarpcontinued-customizable-time-warp-and-lossless-physics-warp/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:213px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222018-01-29T13:06:56Z\u0022 title=\u002201/29/2018 01:06  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00226 yr\u0022\u003EJanuary 29, 2018\u003C/time\u003E by Rocket In My Pocket\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DStaal","CreatedById":155685,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-01-29T13:52:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHere you go:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed5909459726\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/138848-131-historian-expanded/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:214px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou may or may not want to disable overlays.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}